{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The Strange City</i> is a single-player horror adventure game that invites you into a world of eerie mysteries and strange discoveries.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>The Strange City</i>\u2014A World of Mystery, Fear, and Survival</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944750/extras/STC_GIF_intro_00.gif?t=1734401700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On an unsettling night, Agent G awakens after a brutal car crash. Disoriented and alone, she notices two mysterious lights drifting into the forest. Compelled by an inexplicable force, G ventures deeper into the unknown. Only by reaching the end of this haunting path will she uncover the true reason for her adventure\u2014and the secrets that await in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Each Chapter Challenges You to Adapt and Think on Your Feet</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944750/extras/STC_GIF_Challenges_01.gif?t=1734401700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>The Strange City</i>, survival demands more than courage\u2014it requires wit.<i> </i>Across five chapters, relentless pursuers each employ unique hunting tactics to track G. To endure, you must outsmart their unyielding chase, search the fear-filled environments, and uncover the escape route!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Only Those Who Break Their Limits Will Survive</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944750/extras/STC_GIF_BossRun_02.gif?t=1734401700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survival won\u2019t come easy\u2014each chapter culminates in a final encounter that will push your instincts and resolve to limits. Only those who conquer these final trials can move forward to the next chapter of the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Uncover the Secrets of <i>The Strange City</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944750/extras/STC_GIF_mystery_03.gif?t=1734401700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What will she find waiting at the end of the path? Dive into <i>The Strange City</i> and discover the reason behind G\u2019s fateful adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>*Photosensitivity Seizure Warning - Please read this notice before playing.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A few people may experience seizures when exposed to flashing lights or visual patterns in video games. Even individuals without a history of seizures or epilepsy may experience a condition known as &quot;photosensitive epilepsy&quot; when playing video games.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Failed surgery","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944750/e4b02a09baf6b4546a1af09917a4f3f1e67b71ec.jpg"},{"name":"Father","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944750/07aa220ef684ba3b2fe2cce68007f64c3d780cb1.jpg"},{"name":"Butcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944750/2eac5c465dbaa01eb61486baed4609c08a77e63f.jpg"},{"name":"Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944750/c9f233966e9dac99bffd2b91916f6a24f53c13f4.jpg"},{"name":"Blind faith","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944750/30f0e758866359d7edb406b4c6e437c0f9f21180.jpg"},{"name":"Eyesight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2944750/2713170445f1eb4dfa7dd84d239da90b600c9deb.jpg"},{"name":"Staring contest","path":"https://